deas, no mention of calm, reliability.\n\nThus B seems strongest overall despite attitude. Might be best candidate.\n\nWe could ask others about any missing info like A's calmness, D's weather skill, etc. But we have all attributes. So we can vote B.\n\nWe should also note that B's weak memory for numbers could be mitigated by using avionics, but we cannot mitigate per rules. We must weigh as evidence.\n\nThus final answer: vote for Candidate B.\n\nPublic message: summarize reasoning, highlight strengths and weaknesses, compare, conclude."}
